Emotion Recognition App - README
Overview
This Emotion Recognition App utilizes a fine-tuned ResNet50 model to identify human emotions from facial images. It's designed to process and predict emotions like Angry, Disgust, Fear, Happy, Sad, Surprise, and Neutral.

Features
Image Upload: Users can upload an image to be analyzed.
Emotion Prediction: The app predicts the emotion of the face in the image.
Heatmap Generation: Provides a heatmap for visualizing areas influencing the prediction.